description:
The `sdk.updateProfile(properties)` method updates the profile associated with the **authenticated user**.
The `properties` object contains the following information: 
```
{
  birthday: '06/07/1990';
  gender: 0;
  fibricheck_info:
   app: {
      version: appVersion,
    },
    device: {
      os: deviceOSVersion,
      model: deviceModel,
      type: deviceSystemName,
      manufacturer: deviceManufacturer,
    }
  }
}
```
